---
---

<section id="about" class="py-24 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div>
        <p class="text-secondary uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-xs font-semibold mb-5">Our Story</p>
        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl text-charcoal mb-7 leading-tight">
          Where Culinary Art Meets Meticulous Craft
        </h2>
        <p class="text-charcoal/65 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-5">
          The Culinary Accountant brings the same precision and care to every plate that a skilled
          accountant brings to every line item. Every menu is thoughtfully designed, every ingredient
          carefully sourced, and every detail accounted for.
        </p>
        <p class="text-charcoal/65 leading-relaxed mb-10">
          Based in Charlotte, NC, we create memorable dining experiences for events of all sizes —
          from intimate dinner parties to grand celebrations. When you trust us with your event,
          nothing is left to chance.
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-primary font-medium">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M12 2C8.13 2 5 5.13 5 9c0 5.25 7 13 7 13s7-7.75 7-13c0-3.87-3.13-7-7-7z" />
            <circle cx="12" cy="9" r="2.5" />
          </svg>
          <span>Charlotte, North Carolina</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative">
        <div
          class="aspect-[3/4] rounded-2xl flex flex-col items-center justify-center"
          style="background: linear-gradient(145deg, #edf7e5 0%, #d0ebbe 100%);"
        >
          <svg width="72" height="72" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#2D5A1B" stroke-width="0.8" opacity="0.35">
            <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2" />
            <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4" />
            <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87" />
            <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75" />
          </svg>
          <p class="text-primary/35 text-xs font-medium tracking-wider uppercase mt-3">Chef photo coming soon</p>
        </div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-5 -right-5 w-28 h-28 rounded-2xl bg-secondary/15 -z-10"></div>
        <div class="absolute -top-5 -left-5 w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-primary/8 -z-10"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
